org.opencyc.cycobject
Class CycListParser

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.opencyc.cycobject.CycListParser
public class CycListParser
extends java.lang.Object

Provides a parser that reads a String representation and constructs the corresponding CycList. Has a weakness in that quoted strings must not contain embedded newlines.
